(5, 'Star_Wars_Episode_2_Atacke_of_the_Clone.jpg', 'Фильм 2002 года.', 'Star Wars: Episode II - Attack of the Clones', 'MIDNIGHT!!!!!', '^_^', '', '<pre>\r\nТреклист:\r\nCD 1 (Original Realise)\r\n01. John Williams - Star Wars Main Title And Ambush on Coruscant\r\n02. John Williams - Love Theme from Attack of the Clones\r\n03. John Williams - Zam the Assassin and The Chase Through Coruscant\r\n04. John Williams - Yoda and the Younglings\r\n05. John Williams - Departing Coruscant\r\n06. John Williams - Anakin and PadmPi\r\n07. John Williams - Jango''s Escape\r\n08. John Williams - The Meadow Picnic\r\n09. John Williams - Bounty Hunter''s Pursuit\r\n10. John Williams - Return to Tatooine\r\n11. John Williams - The Tusken Camp and The Homestead\r\n12. John Williams - Love Pledge and The Arena\r\n13. John Williams - Confrontation with Count Dooku and Finale\r\n14. John Williams - On the Conveyor Belt\r\nCD 2 (The Extended Edition)\r\n01. John Williams - 20th Century Fox Fanfare\r\n02. John Williams - Star Wars Main Titles\r\n03. John Williams - Old Friends\r\n04. John Williams - Assasination Attempt And Speeder Chase\r\n05. John Williams - The Chase Through Coruscant Continues\r\n06. John Williams - The Assasin''s Demise\r\n07. John Williams - Growing Up\r\n08. John Williams - Departing Coruscant\r\n09. John Williams - Dex''s Diner\r\n10. John Williams - Yoda And The Younglings\r\n11. John Williams - Arrival At Kamino\r\n12. John Williams - Forbidden Kiss\r\n13. John Williams - The Clone Army\r\n14. John Williams - The Meadow Picnic\r\n15. John Williams - Meeting Jango Fett\r\n16. John Williams - Anakin And Padme\r\n17. John Williams - Mystery Of The Clones\r\n18. John Williams - Tatooine Resolution\r\n19. John Williams - Jango vs. Obi-Wan\r\n20. John Williams - Bounty Hunter''s Pursuit\r\n21. John Williams - Anakin''s Search\r\n22. John Williams - Dark Deeds\r\nCD 3 (The Extended Edition)\r\n01. John Williams - Anakin''s Confession\r\n02. John Williams - Emergency Powers\r\n03. John Williams - Count Dooku''s Offer\r\n04. John Williams - Landing On Geonosis\r\n05. John Williams - The Droids Confer\r\n06. John Williams - Inside The Droid Factory\r\n07. John Williams - Love Pledge\r\n08. John Williams - The Fight Begins\r\n09. John Williams - Arrival Of The Jedi\r\n10. John Williams - Encircled\r\n11. John Williams - Attack Of The Clones\r\n12. John Williams - The Battle Of Geonosis\r\n13. John Williams - Secret Plans\r\n14. John Williams - Dooku''s Escape\r\n15. John Williams - Chasing The Seperatists\r\n16. John Williams - Confrontation With The Sith\r\n17. John Williams - Padme''s Orders\r\n18. John Williams - The Duel Continues\r\n19. John Williams - Knowledge Of The Force\r\n20. John Williams - Yoda vs. Dooku\r\n21. John Williams - Yoda''s Troubles\r\n22. John Williams - Secrect Marriage And Finale\r\n23. John Williams - End Credits\r\nCD 4 (The Extended Edition)\r\n01. John Williams - Album Introduction\r\n02. John Williams - Attack Of The Clones [Music Video]\r\n03. John Williams - Across The Stars [Introduction]\r\n04. John Williams - [Archival Bonus Track]: Across The Stars (Dialogue Version)\r\n05. John Williams - Geonosis Love Medley\r\n06. John Williams - On The Conveyor Belt\r\n07. John Williams - Arena Source [Ben Burtt]\r\n08. John Williams - Attack Of The Clones Orchestral Suite\r\n09. John Williams - The Story Of Episode II\r\n</pre>'),
(6, 'Star_Wars_Episode_3_Revenge_of_the_Sith.jpg', 'Фильм 2005 года', 'Star Wars: Episode III - Revenge of the Sith', 'asas', '', '', '<pre>\r\nТреклист:\r\nCD 1 (OST)\r\n01. John Williams - Star Wars And The Revenge Of The Sith\r\n02. John Williams - Anakin''s Dream\r\n03. John Williams - Battle Of The Heroes\r\n04. John Williams - Anakin''s Betrayal\r\n05. John Williams - General Grievous\r\n06. John Williams - Palpatine''s Teachings\r\n07. John Williams - Grievous And The Droids\r\n08. John Williams - Padme''s Ruminations\r\n09. John Williams - Anakin Vs. Obi-Wan\r\n10. John Williams - Anakin''s Dark Deeds\r\n11. John Williams - Enter Lord Vader\r\n12. John Williams - The Immolation Scene\r\n13. John Williams - Grievous Speaks To Lord Sidious\r\n14. John Williams - The Birth Of The Twins And Padme''s Destiny\r\n15. John Williams - A New Hope And End Credits\r\nCD 2 (The Extended Edition)\r\n01. John Williams - 20th Century Fox Fanfare\r\n02. John Williams - Star Wars Main Title / Battle Over Coruscant\r\n03. John Williams - Enter General Grevious\r\n04. John Williams - Dooku''s Entrance\r\n05. John Williams - Escape With The Chancellor\r\n06. John Williams - Jedi vs. Droids\r\n07. John Williams - Another Happy Landing\r\n08. John Williams - The Chancellor''s Arrival\r\n09. John Williams - Lovers'' Reunion\r\n10. John Williams - Travelling To Utapau / Anakin''s Dream\r\n11. John Williams - Dreams And Visions\r\n12. John Williams - Be Careful Of Your Friend\r\n13. John Williams - On The Council\r\n14. John Williams - We''re At War\r\n15. John Williams - The Prophecy\r\n16. John Williams - The Tragedy Of Darth Plagueis\r\n17. John Williams - Kashyyyk\r\n18. John Williams - Goodbye Old Friend\r\n19. John Williams - Daydreams\r\n20. John Williams - Arrival At Utapau\r\n21. John Williams - Riding Boga\r\n22. John Williams - Crushing The Droids\r\n23. John Williams - Obi-Wan vs. Grievous\r\n24. John Williams - Jedi War Council\r\n25. John Williams - Palpatine''s Seducti